column2: BRING BACK JOHNNY!!!!
column26: Bring back Johnny Depp as Gellert Grindelwald in the fantastic beasts franchise
column33: Warner Brothers: Bring back Johnny Depp as Gellert Grindelwald in the fantastic beasts franchise
column34:
Johnny Depp has just been fired from the fantastic beasts franchise after losing the case with British news paper the Sun for calling him a wife-beater in 2018 after his ex-wife Amber Heard accused him for physically and mentally abusing her.

The claims of Amber Heard being abused by Johnny depp are yet to be proven, what has been proven that at least a part of Heard's story is fake. She has faked her wounds using make-up, she even admitted that she has abused depp in the past. and She however is still planned to star in Warner Brother's Aquaman 2 as Mera.

Johnny depp sued newspaper the Sun after they published an artical which originally carried the headline “Gone Potty: How can JK Rowling be ‘genuinely happy’ casting wife beater Johnny Depp in the new Fantastic Beasts film?”. Depp however lost this trial on 2 November 2020 becuase when the artical was published there wasn't enough proof that Depp wasn't a "wife-beater". Shortly after this Depp stated on his Instagram that Warner Brothers had asked him to resign form his role as Grindelwald in the fantastic beasts franchise, meaning that they're planning to recast him. Because of this Fantastic Beasts 3 has also been moved back for a second time to the summer of 2022, originally it should've been released this November.

We want justice for Johnny Depp and for him to return as Gellert Grindelwald.
column36: Bring back Johnny Depp as Gellert Grindelwald in the fantastic beasts franchise

column33: Warner Brothers: Bring back Johnny Depp as Gellert Grindelwald in the fantastic beasts franchise
column34:
Johnny Depp has just been fired from the fantastic beasts franchise after losing the case with British news paper the Sun for calling him a wife-beater in 2018 after his ex-wife Amber Heard accused him for physically and mentally abusing her.

The claims of Amber Heard being abused by Johnny depp are yet to be proven, what has been proven that at least a part of Heard's story is fake. She has faked her wounds using make-up, she even admitted that she has abused depp in the past. and She however is still planned to star in Warner Brother's Aquaman 2 as Mera.

Johnny depp sued newspaper the Sun after they published an artical which originally carried the headline “Gone Potty: How can JK Rowling be ‘genuinely happy’ casting wife beater Johnny Depp in the new Fantastic Beasts film?”. Depp however lost this trial on 2 November 2020 becuase when the artical was published there wasn't enough proof that Depp wasn't a "wife-beater". Shortly after this Depp stated on his Instagram that Warner Brothers had asked him to resign form his role as Grindelwald in the fantastic beasts franchise, meaning that they're planning to recast him. Because of this Fantastic Beasts 3 has also been moved back for a second time to the summer of 2022, originally it should've been released this November.

We want justice for Johnny Depp and for him to return as Gellert Grindelwald.
